{"tid":117202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯達英超2000分里程碑","createTime":"2017-02-12T04:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T12:38:54.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73dafb9b5a07ed1d299703b3411f7b0b43009ed2","tid":117202,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"曼聯周六英超寫下新里程碑，在主場2:0輕取屈福特後，成為首支在英超累積2000分的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n自英超1992年創立後，曼聯長年是此聯賽的霸主，共贏得13次錦標，雖然費格遜退休後，戰績不及過去彪炳，但周六戰勝屈福特後，已達到一項新的里程碑，就是成為首支在英超到達2000分的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n紅魔在949場英超中，取得599勝203和147負的佳績，領先第2位的阿仙奴多達203分，而第3至第6位的球隊，順序是車路士、利物浦、熱刺及愛華頓。<br />\n<br />\n另外，曼聯目前已16場聯賽不敗，只要下月4日在主場對般尼茅夫延續勝績，便會成為第1支取得600場英超勝仗的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n英超累積分數排行榜<br />\n<br />\n球隊 分數<br />\n<br />\n1.曼聯 2000<br />\n<br />\n2.阿仙奴 1797<br />\n<br />\n3.車路士 1755<br />\n<br />\n4.利物浦 1647<br />\n<br />\n5.熱刺 1411<br />\n<br />\n6.愛華頓 1304"},{"pid":"f4fa164f2c51827084d885d93190b1fed2510ae9","tid":117202,"uid":7009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"但都係第6"},{"pid":"fc7cebe36c808164fb489198e234860fc6f70594","tid":117202,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"阿狗第二高分 得兩個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b79965104c05c641fc85c85312e0e60b5526ba","tid":117202,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但都係第6</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0649bc03a675c58de30acb086df70cf25a745a23","tid":117202,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e56bcb13d2bedb5d3383899bdd84341fd2d82b8","tid":117202,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>阿狗第二高分 得兩個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bl